## Day 11 - July 11, 2026: Cryptography Core Content

Covered: Encryption process, Symmetric Encryption (AES/3DES/Blowfish/
Twofish), Asymmetric Encryption (RSA/ECC/Diffie-Hellman/ElGamal), 
Hashing (MD5/SHA-1/SHA-256), Hash Extensions (HMAC/Salting), 
Digital Signature (RSA/DSA).

### Symmetric vs Asymmetric - Quick Reference
| Characteristic | Symmetric | Asymmetric |
|---|---|---|
| Processing | Fast | Slow |
| Key Size | Small | Large |
| Scalability | Low | High |
| Key Exchange | Problem | Solved |

### Digital Signature Flow
Message -> Hash -> Sign with PRIVATE key -> Verify with PUBLIC key
(proves authenticity + integrity)

